query: Could you devise a 7-day trip itinerary for two people starting in Baltimore and covering 3 cities in Texas from March 18th to March 24th, 2022? Our budget is now set at $6,700 for this trip. We require accommodations that allow smoking, and we are interested in trying Mexican, Italian, French, and Chinese cuisines. We will not be self-driving, so please include other available modes of transportation in the itinerary.
